container of rigid construction and rectangular configuration; 
fitted with devices permitting its ready handling, particularly 
its transfer from one mode of transport to another; so designed 
to be readily filled and emptied; intended to contain one or more 
articles of cargo or bulk commodities for transportation by water 
and one or more other transport modes. The term includes 
