intent. Comments received during this outreach have been considered in developing this proposal. Other provisions
in section 2503 of the Energy Policy Act prescribe specific regulatory initiatives regarding the removal or on-site
reprocessing of abandoned coal refuse sites. These initiatives will be implemented under a separate rulemaking.


